background = "Mortimer lived his entire life working for different criminal organizations in the city. What many would consider illegal and immoral, Mortimer sees it as an average Tuesday. It’s a difficult life, but after recently taking over the lead criminal gang in the city, Mortimer is desperate to step up and do a good job to lead his new group, and all the people he suddenly finds that are depending on him for survival."
